{"tid":1381081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你地老母 君子報仇十年未晚 但係d post就唔撚見哂 唔講我以為葉虎已經證實唔關事","createTime":"2019-07-29T07:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T16:22:38.000Z","uid":220864,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d65821d97a7f4ef19c46ffbd9073c2902c86790b","tid":1381081,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:13:02.000Z","msg":"好多大事都唔夠集中推<br />\n一個post都推唔完<br />\n屌你老個d咩推到佢仆街呢?<br />\n潘杰大仆街都開到29<br />\n<br />\n咁多大事連2都去唔到呀屌你地<br />\n葉虎<br />\n射向老人院<br />\n鄉黑勾結<br />\n何妖話佢地係英雄呢?<br />\n重有好撚多呀唔一一論述<br />\n無錯今日你可以加埋個南非女人比人推底落去<br />\n但係之前d帳都未撚算<br />\n就全部無人提！！！！<br />\n<br />\n我係林鄭都心諗<br />\n屌你唔撚洗回應啦<br />\n過一日你地都唔撚記得哂<br />\n佢一定心諗：驚閪咩！"},{"pid":"d8814045989f5c7d0d8b8b38fde05c29a9b47747","tid":1381081,"uid":220864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:13:43.000Z","msg":"推佢老母"},{"pid":"d6eef23f81de64793b1a28b794f1c58c0d1d3a7c","tid":1381081,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"屌哂你地老母"},{"pid":"8fc67383c7867e5cdac6aae25ec3f72ef1013d31","tid":1381081,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:15:24.000Z","msg":"舊帳全部唔撚算咩"},{"pid":"7349442c421602bb299d12815c2a2273a78f870d","tid":1381081,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e0086a1fedf45e036a090774b9dfba96fa205a","tid":1381081,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8814045989f5c7d0d8b8b38fde05c29a9b47747","tid":1381081,"uid":220864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:13:43.000Z","msg":"推佢老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6712d789b53c0c1af2614cdb77e2251a8ec4caba","tid":1381081,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl